---
title: Bacon & Prawn Singapore-Style Noodles with Veggies & Spring Onion
description: Get ready for a dish that takes your palate on a whirlwind adventure through the bustling streets of Southeast Asia! Oodles of noodles are wrapped up in a blend of oyster and soy sauces, tossed through with colourful veggies and perfectly pan-seared prawns. Who needs takeaway when homemade tastes so good?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
